# Backend (Express + SQLite)

1. Install:
   cd backend
   npm install

2. Create .env (copy .env.example) and set JWT_SECRET & FRONTEND_ORIGIN if needed.

3. Seed users:
   npm run seed

4. Start server:
   npm start
   # or for dev:
   npm run dev

Server will run on PORT (default 4000). API base: http://localhost:4000/api

Endpoints:
- POST /api/register {name,email,password}
- POST /api/login {email,password}
- GET  /api/slots?from=YYYY-MM-DD&to=YYYY-MM-DD
- POST /api/book {slotId}  (requires Bearer token, patient)
- GET  /api/my-bookings  (patient)
- GET  /api/all-bookings (admin)
